<div class='spoiler'>
<a class="spoiler" href="/questions/1283704-the-premise-is-so-weak-we-don-t-get-any">This question contains spoilers...</a>
<span class='spoilerAnswerText'>
<a class="jsShowSpoiler spoilerAction">(view spoiler)</a><span class="spoilerContainer" style="display: none">[The premise is so weak. We don't get any explanation of how the jury could convict him. No evidence is provided. Will that all come out or is this story full of holes? <a class="jsHideSpoiler spoilerAction">(hide spoiler)</a>]</span>
</span>
