<span class='communityAnswerText'>
<span class="expandableContainer"><span class="truncatedContent">The book wasn&apos;t about the verdict... it&apos;s about relationships. It&apos;s about how tenuous relationships can be without adding what happened... it&apos;s wonder<a class="jsShow showAction" href="#">…more</a></span><span class="fullContent">The book wasn't about the verdict... it's about relationships. It's about how tenuous relationships can be without adding what happened... it's wondering if the end was inevitable without the middle.<a class="jsHide hideAction" href="#">(less)</a></span></span>
