<span id="freeTextContainer17528654746749046455">this is an entirely character driven novel. there is no plot beyond what you read in the synopsis - what propels this book is a study of the characters feelings and motivations. and i would have found this story compelling if i had liked the characters. but unfortunately i didnt, so this was quite a boring reading experience for me personally.<br/><br/>i do like that this story attempts to explore topics such as what a marriage means, how relationships between people go because just a formal union, how ci</span>
  <span id="freeText17528654746749046455" style="display:none">this is an entirely character driven novel. there is no plot beyond what you read in the synopsis - what propels this book is a study of the characters feelings and motivations. and i would have found this story compelling if i had liked the characters. but unfortunately i didnt, so this was quite a boring reading experience for me personally.<br /><br />i do like that this story attempts to explore topics such as what a marriage means, how relationships between people go because just a formal union, how circumstance is a key factor in life, and the desire to take care of others. but while i found these themes interesting, the characters who encompassed them are not, therefore the execution fell short. <br /><br />overall, this isnt a terrible book but i do wish i had a better connection to the characters, who are the sole purpose of the story. <br /><br /><b>↠ <i>2.5 stars</i></b></span>
