        <div class="reviewText stacked">
              <span id="reviewTextContainer2368967044" class="readable"
              >
            
<span id="freeTextContainer4717787077362006234">The strongest writing I&apos;ve read in a while. Witty in all the right places. Rich characters. The plot isn&apos;t ultra-memorable but I have the feeling it&apos;s going to haunt me the more I think about it. There&apos;s a lot of overt conflict, internal and external, but the ever-present social subtext is what makes it art. Glad I didn&apos;t miss it!</span>
  <span id="freeText4717787077362006234" style="display:none">The strongest writing I've read in a while. Witty in all the right places. Rich characters. The plot isn't ultra-memorable but I have the feeling it's going to haunt me the more I think about it. There's a lot of overt conflict, internal and external, but the ever-present social subtext is what makes it art. Glad I didn't miss it!</span>
